Arts Documentary hosted by Mathias Desmarres, published by TV5Monde in 2014 - French narration. 
http://docuwiki.net/images/7/7b/Comme-une-envie-de-moustache-Cover.jpg

Information
------------------------------
Desire for a moustache.

The moustache returns with a vengeance! In the manner of a report with many accounts from the moustachioed, facial hair specialists and archive pictures, the director explores the destiny of this facial ornament. Excited by the desire of sporting one, he offers us a joyously off-beat look at contemporary virility.
